Class LevelProjectileManager

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.projectiles.ProjectileManager
com.example.demo.managers.LevelProjectileManager
public class LevelProjectileManager extends ProjectileManager
Manages projectiles in a level, including user and enemy projectiles.
